<div style="text-align: right;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">rating:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+73</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="I like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="I don't like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="Cancel my vote" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="text-align: center; margin: auto; width: 240px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:linear-gradient(#00cccc, #009494); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>Loading grape_space.x3d</p>
<div style="text-align: center; padding: 2px 20px; color: black; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #fff0f0; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:30px /70px;">
<p>::RENDERING::</p>
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/18-1.gif" alt="18-1.gif" class="image" /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/18-1.gif" alt="18-1.gif" class="image" /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/18-1.gif" alt="18-1.gif" class="image" /></div>
<br /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#6c316c; background:linear-gradient(#562756, #6c316c); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>What are you doing here?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/grape_snark.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="grape_snark.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:linear-gradient(#00cccc, #009494); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>I'm here to talk.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/alex_sad1.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad1.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#6c316c; background:linear-gradient(#562756, #6c316c); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>You came all the way over to lord your superiority over me?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/grape.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="grape.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:linear-gradient(#00cccc, #009494); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>No. I came because you need a friend.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/alex_sad1.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad1.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#6c316c; background:linear-gradient(#562756, #6c316c); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>I'm your friend? So then you're here to kill me too?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/grape_mad.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="grape_mad.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:linear-gradient(#00cccc, #009494); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>Grape&#8230;</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/alex_cry.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_cry.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#6c316c; background:linear-gradient(#562756, #6c316c); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>What? Did you think I'd fall over myself apologizing for telling you how I felt about what you did to Glacon?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/grape_mad.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="grape_mad.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:linear-gradient(#00cccc, #009494); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>No. I&#8230;</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/alex_sad1.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_sad1.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#6c316c; background:linear-gradient(#562756, #6c316c); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>You thought this made us the same? Kindred spirits in murder?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/grape_mad.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="grape_mad.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #f5e9e9; font-size: 8pt; background-color: #009494; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#009494; background:linear-gradient(#00cccc, #009494); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>Do you think you could stop being an asshole for two milliseconds and listen to me?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/alex_angry.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="75px" alt="alex_angry.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px;">
<div style="color: white; font-size: 8pt; border-radius:30px /70px; background:#6c316c; background:linear-gradient(#562756, #6c316c); text-align: left; padding: 2px 20px;">
<p>No. I don't need your self righteous pity. I'll deal with this my way.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/come-back-kid/grape.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="75px" alt="grape.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
